4. Smart Contracts

4.1 DJIAToken.sol

An ERC-20 token representing the DJIA index. Features include:
	â€¢	Minting and Burning: Controlled by the contract owner.
	â€¢	Dividend Distribution: Automated and transparent.

4.2 DJIAOracle.sol

A smart contract that fetches real-time DJIA prices using Chainlink oracles. It ensures secure and accurate price data for the ecosystem.

5. Frontend Architecture

The React-based frontend provides a responsive and user-friendly interface. Key features include:
	â€¢	Dynamic Token Display: Real-time token data through the TokenCard component.
	â€¢	Intuitive Navigation: Modular pages (Home, About, Dashboard) for seamless user experience.
	â€¢	Blockchain Context: Centralized management of blockchain interactions using React Context API.

6. Deployment and Workflow

6.1 Deployment Scripts
	â€¢	deploy-contract.js: Deploys the DJIAToken and DJIAOracle contracts.
	â€¢	update-oracle.js: Updates the oracle with the latest DJIA price.

6.2 CI/CD Integration

GitHub Actions automate testing and deployment pipelines to ensure continuous integration and delivery.

7. Testing Framework

